1
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:40,720
Your Majesty,

2
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,920
someone swapped the medicinal wine

3
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:43,840
for arsenic.

4
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:46,020
The General...

5
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:48,759
has died from poisoning.

6
00:01:50,080 --> 00:01:52,800
They used my hand to poison General Xiao.

7
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:54,600
In this way,

8
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:56,400
A'ling and the Xiao Army

9
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:58,039
will see me as a sworn enemy.

10
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:03,440
Interrogate everyone who knew about today's plan.

11
00:02:03,440 --> 00:02:04,900
After the interrogation,

12
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,760
leave no one alive.

13
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:08,020
Yes, Your Majesty.

14
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:10,120
Back then, Guimian used a secret order

15
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:12,400
to drive a wedge between you and the General.

16
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:14,130
Could it be him again this time?

17
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,880
Is his goal...

18
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:23,400
What is the situation with the Xiao Army?

19
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,660
I have blocked the news

20
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:26,610
of the General's death as planned.

21
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,720
It is stable for now.

22
00:02:29,079 --> 00:02:30,520
Guimian's identity is unknown.

23
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:32,120
We cannot let our guard down.

24
00:02:34,079 --> 00:02:35,140
What about A'ling?

25
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,320
Her Majesty...

26
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:38,380
she is devastated.

27
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,000
A-Ling.

28
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:50,100
The Jiaoyue Sword is gone.

29
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:53,520
Did A-Ling leave the palace?

30
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,040
Young General,

31
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:58,120
since you have returned,

32
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,579
lead us to storm the Palace

33
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:00,880
and kill the Emperor.

34
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:02,880
I came back to tell everyone

35
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:07,180
that there is something suspicious about the Great General's death.

36
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:08,760
However,

37
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,410
how did you two learn

38
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:12,300
the news of my father's death?

39
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,760
This concerns the state.

40
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,760
Li Yunxi would surely suppress the news.

41
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:17,820
It wouldn't reach the camp this fast.

42
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:19,010
It was...

43
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:20,810
Someone told us.

44
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:27,320
If she doesn't take revenge,

45
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:28,480
she's unworthy of being a daughter.

46
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,880
She really has been blinded by the Emperor.

47
00:03:31,079 --> 00:03:32,960
She doesn't deserve to be our Young General.

48
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:33,820
We can't let her

49
00:03:34,079 --> 00:03:35,520
ruin our grand plan.

50
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,860
What's the situation now?

51
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:04,520
The Imperial Guard Division was prepared.

52
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:07,320
They are in a standoff with the Xiao Army right now.

53
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,880
You can't do anything on your own.

54
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:14,000
Just rest for a while.

55
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,240
Only by finding the real killer

56
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,800
can I clear Li Yunxi's name

57
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:18,279
and quell the unrest.

58
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:23,300
You don't believe the Emperor killed General Xiao.

59
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,480
Killing my father

60
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,930
would only incite hatred in the Xiao Army.

61
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,240
He has no reason to do that.

62
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,000
But I heard

63
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,420
it was the late Emperor

64
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,920
who killed your mother and brother.

65
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,600
Between the Xiao family and the Emperor,

66
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:38,400
there has long been a blood feud.

67
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,520
W-What's wrong?

68
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:50,010
How do you know about these things?

69
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:53,650
I've known General Xiao for years.

70
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:55,520
When he was troubled,

71
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:56,880
he told me.

72
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,520
Father kept these matters even from me.

73
00:04:59,520 --> 00:05:00,760
How could he readily

74
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:03,120
confide in an outsider?

75
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:06,860
Is Prince Qi really connected to Ghost Face?

76
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:25,080
You really are in Prince Qi's Manor.

77
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:26,810
You are connected to Prince Qi.

78
00:05:33,159 --> 00:05:35,159
So it was you who sent me the message.

79
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:38,320
I was just verifying my guess.

80
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:42,340
I wanted to see if imitating Hanxing's messages

81
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:43,920
would lure you out.

82
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:51,200
Why do you ignore your blood feud

83
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:54,020
and target me, the one helping you take revenge?

84
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:56,360
Helping me take revenge?

85
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:58,960
I'm afraid you're just using everyone

86
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:00,400
to achieve your own ends.

87
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,400
Hanxing,

88
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:03,800
Consort Xue,

89
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:05,160
Prince Qi,

90
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:06,840
and even my father.

91
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:09,000
They are all just your pawns.

92
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:29,920
Who are you?

93
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:42,720
Hanxing.

94
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:47,840
Hanxing.

95
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:49,780
How could it be you?

96
00:06:52,440 --> 00:06:53,300
Your Highness.

97
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:56,340
Is it true that as long as Ghost Face dies,

98
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:58,920
you will be at ease?

99
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,450
You clearly aren't Ghost Face.

100
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,240
Why die for him?

101
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,080
Because...

102
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,360
I hope Master

103
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:10,760
gets what she wants.

104
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:22,160
What is this?

105
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:25,480
For the Little Prince.

106
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:28,480
Hanxing.

107
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,600
Actually, I didn't...

108
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:33,000
Though the night is cold,

109
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,920
the starry sky

110
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,800
is truly beautiful.

111
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:02,090
Hanxing has Muscle-Softening Powder on her.

112
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:14,840
Do it.

113
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:15,920
Understood.

114
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:29,200
It's actually you.

115
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:56,840
You knew I suspected you,

116
00:08:57,120 --> 00:09:00,050
yet you still had Hanxing come here disguised as you,

117
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,960
using my hand to kill her.

118
00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:05,960
She was useless.

119
00:09:06,640 --> 00:09:08,700
She couldn't even be a proper double.

120
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:11,840
Just like I never thought...

121
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:14,560
I have to treat you like this.

122
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:15,560
You...

123
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:20,280
You've been dosed with Soft Muscle Powder.

124
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:25,760
Li Yunmo.

125
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:28,640
I feel like I never knew you at all.

126
00:09:30,760 --> 00:09:32,240
We could have been like before,

127
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,520
as close as ever.

128
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:34,280
It was you.

129
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:36,600
You ruined everything.

130
00:09:37,760 --> 00:09:38,440
I...

131
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:41,770
Why did you have to dig so deep into Ghost Face?

132
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:43,860
You could have just

133
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,560
been like your father

134
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:46,840
and hated Li Yunxi.

135
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:48,480
Let go.

136
00:09:50,160 --> 00:09:51,320
So it was you.

137
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:54,480
To make me hate Li Yunxi,

138
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:57,320
you replaced the medicine in the wine with arsenic

139
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,600
and killed my father.

140
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,840
I did kill Xiao Rushan.

141
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:04,450
I thought you and Li Yunxi would turn against each other.

142
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,960
But the first thing you did when you woke up

143
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:08,200
was to find the real killer

144
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,660
and clear Li Yunxi's name.

145
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,160
Xiao Ling.

146
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,600
I'm so disappointed in you.

147
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:18,120
Why do you want Li Yunxi dead so badly?

148
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:20,090
Because he doesn't deserve it.

149
00:10:21,560 --> 00:10:24,360
He doesn't deserve everything he has.

150
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,360
You did everything you could

151
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:28,490
to turn the Xiao Army against Li Yunxi.

152
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:30,120
All for the throne.

153
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:31,240
The throne.

154
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:35,620
The Late Emperor committed so many sins.

155
00:10:35,760 --> 00:10:38,120
Shouldn't Li Yunxi pay for his father's debts?

156
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:40,400
He was just a sickly Crown Prince back then.

157
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:41,920
He was powerless to stop the Late Emperor.

158
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:44,320
The more you defend him, the more I hate him.

159
00:10:52,560 --> 00:10:53,960
So you imprisoned me

160
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:57,120
to threaten Li Yunxi.

161
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,000
Xiao Ling.

162
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,160
I want the throne.

163
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:06,840
And I want you.

164
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:11,800
I want it, too.

165
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:22,240
Why?

166
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:25,040
Why is it you?

167
00:11:26,640 --> 00:11:27,680
Li Yunmo.
